  "text": "With the goal of understanding the motion of actin filaments in a model for the cytoskeleton proposed in [CITATION_1] , we consider a collection of particles moving in one space dimension with fixed velocity v either to the left or to the right. Denoting their densities by u r and u l , for right and left moving filaments, respectively, this reads",
